'''第一次鼠疫大流行'''（英文：First Plague Pandemic），也称'''[[中世纪前期|中世纪前期]]瘟疫'''（Early Medieval Pandemic），是[[旧大陆|旧大陆]]的第一次[[鼠疫|鼠疫]][[大流行|大流行]]，由[[鼠疫桿菌|鼠疫杆菌]]致病<ref name=":2">{{Cite web|title=The History of Plague – Part 1. The Three Great Pandemics|url=https://jmvh.org/article/the-history-of-plague-part-1-the-three-great-pandemics/|access-date=2021-01-15|website=jmvh.org}}</ref>。541年，[[查士丁尼大瘟疫|查士丁尼大瘟疫]]成为此次大流行的开端，直至750年或767年才结束<ref name=":2" />。查士丁尼大瘟疫共造成1500万-1亿人死亡（约25%-60%欧洲人口）<ref>{{Cite journal|title=The Justinianic Plague: An inconsequential pandemic?|url=https://www.pnas.org/content/116/51/25546|last=Mordechai|first=Lee|last2=Eisenberg|first2=Merle|date=2019-12-17|journal=Proceedings of the National Academy of Sciences|issue=51|doi=10.1073/pnas.1903797116|volume=116|pages=25546–25554|language=en|issn=0027-8424|pmid=31792176|last3=Newfield|first3=Timothy P.|last4=Izdebski|first4=Adam|last5=Kay|first5=Janet E.|last6=Poinar|first6=Hendrik}}</ref><ref name=":02">{{Cite journal|title=Top 10 Terrible Epidemics|author=Ishaan Tharoor|url=http://content.time.com/time/specials/packages/article/0,28804,2027479_2027486_2027546,00.html|last=|first=|date=2010-10-26|journal=《[[时代杂志|时代杂志]]》（''Time''）|issue=|doi=|others=|year=|volume=|page=|language=en-US|issn=0040-781X|pmid=}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=An Empire's Epidemic|url=https://www.ph.ucla.edu/epi/bioter/anempiresepidemic.html|accessdate=2020-12-07|author=|date=|format=|work=|publisher=[[加州大学洛杉矶分校|加州大学洛杉矶分校]]（UCLA）|language=}}</ref>。此后，有记录的还有15-18波主要疫情<ref>{{Citation|last=Arrizabalaga|first=Jon|title=plague and epidemics|url=https://www.oxfordreference.com/view/10.1093/acref/9780198662624.001.0001/acref-9780198662624-e-4645|work=The Oxford Dictionary of the Middle Ages|year=2010|editor-last=Bjork|editor-first=Robert E.|publisher=Oxford University Press|language=en|doi=10.1093/acref/9780198662624.001.0001|isbn=978-0-19-866262-4|quote=The first - called the Plague of Justinian and described by Procopius - spread through Europe and Asia Minor from Egypt in 541 and included fifteen epidemics until 767|access-date=2020-05-16}}</ref><ref>{{Citation|last=Stathakopoulos|first=Dionysios|title=Plague, Justinianic (Early Medieval Pandemic)|url=https://www.oxfordreference.com/view/10.1093/acref/9780198662778.001.0001/acref-9780198662778-e-3757|work=[[牛津古典时代晚期词典|The Oxford Dictionary of Late Antiquity]]|year=2018|publisher=Oxford University Press|language=en|doi=10.1093/acref/9780198662778.001.0001|isbn=978-0-19-866277-8|quote=bubonic plague that began in 541 and returned in some eighteen waves (approximately one every twelve years) until 750|access-date=2020-05-16}}</ref>。 第一次鼠疫大流行主要影响了[[地中海盆地|地中海盆地]]的国家，但也感染了[[近东|近东]]和[[北欧|北欧]]的部分地区<ref name=":0">{{Citation|last=Stathakopoulos|first=Dionysios|title=Plague, Justinianic (Early Medieval Pandemic)|url=https://www.oxfordreference.com/view/10.1093/acref/9780198662778.001.0001/acref-9780198662778-e-3757|work=[[牛津古典时代晚期词典|The Oxford Dictionary of Late Antiquity]]|year=2018|publisher=Oxford University Press|language=en|doi=10.1093/acref/9780198662778.001.0001|isbn=978-0-19-866277-8|access-date=2020-05-16}}</ref>。[[罗马帝国|罗马帝国]]皇帝[[查士丁尼一世|查士丁尼一世]]的名字时常被作为[[古典时代晚期|古典时代晚期]]疫情的统称，也包括最早的“查士丁尼大瘟疫”。

